{
  "title": "Delicate Sour Algerian Chicken Tagine",
  "description": "A sour and aerated solo dinner dish featuring almond butter and shio cure, this Algerian chicken tagine is a unique and flavorful meal option, made with raw friendly ingredients for a healthy twist.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
